Captures flow metadata:
src/dst IP, port, protocol,
pd decision code (1/2/3)." style="rounded=1;arcSize=5;fillColor=#E3EFFC;strokeColor=#1A66B5;fontColor=#0C3F75;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=1.5;" vertex="1" parent="11">
