        <mxCell id="24" value="🛡️ C-VEN
Sends heartbeat to PCE
every ~5 minutes.
Includes VEN version,
enforcement mode, status." style="rounded=1;arcSize=5;fillColor=#E3EFFC;strokeColor=#1A66B5;fontColor=#0C3F75;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=1.5;" vertex="1" parent="23">
          <mxGeometry x="15" y="45" width="310" height="155" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="25" value="🖥️ PCE API Layer
Receives heartbeat.
Updates VEN status
and last-seen timestamp
in workload inventory." style="rounded=1;arcSize=5;fillColor=#EDE9FD;strokeColor=#5B4CC4;fontColor=#3B2E8A;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=1.5;" vertex="1" parent="23">
          <mxGeometry x="355" y="45" width="310" height="155" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="26" value="✅ Status: Online

Heartbeat received
within last ~15 min.
Enforcement confirmed
active on this node." style="rounded=1;arcSize=5;fillColor=#E4F5E2;strokeColor=#2E7D32;fontColor=#1B4D1D;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=1.5;" vertex="1" parent="23">
          <mxGeometry x="715" y="45" width="280" height="120" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="27" value="⚠️ Status: Stale

3+ missed heartbeats
(~15 min no contact).
PCE flags as Stale.
STALE ≠ NOT ENFORCING
Local cache still active!" style="rounded=1;arcSize=5;fillColor=#FEF0DA;strokeColor=#9B5E0C;fontColor=#6B3D06;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeWidth=1.5;" vertex="1" parent="23">
          <mxGeometry x="715" y="185" width="280" height="120" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="28" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;strokeWidth=2.5;strokeColor=#1A66B5;endArrow=block;endFill=1;fontFamily=Arial;fontSize=10;fontColor=#1A66B5;fontStyle=1;rounded=1;" edge="1" source="24" target="25" parent="23">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="29" value="heartbeat
received" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;strokeWidth=1.5;strokeColor=#2E7D32;endArrow=block;endFill=1;fontFamily=Arial;fontSize=10;fontColor=#2E7D32;fontStyle=1;rounded=1;" edge="1" source="25" target="26" parent="23">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="30" value="heartbeat
missed 3x" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;strokeWidth=1.5;strokeColor=#9B5E0C;endArrow=block;endFill=1;fontFamily=Arial;fontSize=10;fontColor=#9B5E0C;fontStyle=1;rounded=1;" edge="1" source="25" target="27" parent="23">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="31" value="🔴  KEY OPERATIONAL NOTES

STALE ≠ NOT ENFORCING:  A C-VEN marked Stale in PCE is still enforcing iptables rules from its local Storage Pod cache.
  Do NOT unpair a C-VEN just because PCE shows it as Stale — first verify the pod is actually gone from the cluster.

406 THROTTLING IMPACT:  If PCE returns 406 on telemetry uploads, flow records buffer in Storage Pod locally.
  Storage Pod buffer overflow causes permanent flow record loss for that time window — visible as near-zero pd counts in Splunk.

STORAGE POD ETCD HEALTH:  kubectl exec &lt;storage-pod&gt; -n illumio-system -- etcdctl endpoint health
  Unhealthy etcd (error: user name is empty / WAL lock failures) = no policy updates AND no telemetry upload.
  Root cause of the April 2026 PCE performance incident at Huntington." style="rounded=1;arcSize=3;fillColor=#FDE8E0;strokeColor=#C14B1A;fontColor=#8A2E0A;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;spacingLeft=8;strokeWidth=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="0" y="832" width="1600" height="160" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="32" value="📊  KEY SPLUNK QUERIES

Blocked flows:     index=illumio sourcetype=illumio:flow pd=2 | stats count by src_labels,dst_labels,dst_port | sort -count
Unknown flows:     index=illumio sourcetype=illumio:flow pd=3 | where like(dst_labels, E-PD-scope) | stats count by src_labels,dst_labels,dst_port
Decision trend:    index=illumio sourcetype=illumio:flow | timechart span=30m count by pd
C-VEN heartbeat:   index=illumio sourcetype=illumio:ven_event event_type=heartbeat_failure | stats count by hostname,last_heartbeat" style="rounded=1;arcSize=3;fillColor=#FEF0DA;strokeColor=#9B5E0C;fontColor=#6B3D06;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Arial;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;spacingLeft=8;strokeWidth=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="0" y="1005" width="1600" height="145" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>

      </root>
